<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Token_ring&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Abort Frame">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Abort Frame</span></h3>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
<th>SD</th>
